word_mean_info__list.difference: 指人或事物独具的或奇怪的特点，常带感情色彩。
多指同类事物所共有的特性，一般不用于指人。
最普通用词，既可指有形或无形的特性，又可指个性或共性的特征。
通常指人主观赋予某事物的属性，可指典型事物。
指事物突出引人注目的特点。多用来说明人的容貌特征或地理特征。
指某人或某物天生有别于他人或他物的内部特质或外表特征。
多指一类人或事物所具有的独特的典型的特征。
多指人的性格、心情的特征，尤指先天秉赋的持久的行为模式或性格特征。

bilingual.target: 每个产品的质量都很重要。

bilingual.source: Scientists are researching ways to improve the quality of life.
bilingual.target: 科学家们正在研究提高生活质量的方法。

bilingual.source: If you find any quality issues, please contact Fenghuang Media.
bilingual.target: 如发现印装质量问题，请与凤凰传媒联系。

bilingual.source: Through strict quality assurance, we ensure high product quality.
bilingual.target: 通过严格的质量保证，我们确保产品的高质量。

bilingual.source: Differentiating high-quality products from low-quality ones requires experience.
bilingual.target: 区分高质量产品和低质量产品需要经验。

bilingual.source: Understanding the ctq is essential for quality control.
bilingual.target: 理解关键质量特性对质量控制至关重要。

bilingual.source: Distinguishing between good and bad quality can be challenging.
bilingual.target: 区分好质量和差质量可能是个挑战。

bilingual.source: The company implemented oqc to ensure product quality.
bilingual.target: 公司实施了出货前质量控制以确保产品质量。

list.abstract: quality（英[ˈkwɒləti]，美[ˈkwɑːləti]），英语单词，作名词释义为质量；品质；才能等，作形容词释义为优质的；高品质的等。例句：Its quality is usually guaranteed.（它的质量通常是有保证的。） quality的复数是qualities。短语搭配有air quality（空气质量）、quality control（质量管理）、quality paper（高质量报纸）等。作名词的近义词有talent、capability、ability、identity、character。

yingyinNormal.en: This vinegar added to the quality of the beer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 醋提升了酒的质量。

yingyinNormal.en: New parents deserve quality, affordable childcare.
yingyinNormal.zh: 刚刚做父母的人应该得到高质量，可负担的婴儿保育项目。

yingyinNormal.en: In your lifetime, you will face millions of decisions. The quality of your decisions will determine the quality of your life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在你的一生中你将面对百万个决定。你决定的质量将影响你的生活质量。

yingyinNormal.en: It still creates these expectations that the quality is going to be worse.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们仍然会感觉质量会比全价差。

yingyinNormal.en: So you moved to a better neighborhood. You think this will give you a higher quality of life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你搬去更好的社区，你认为生活质量会更高。

yingyinNormal.en: And it's that mission, that devotion to quality, and ideals, and heart...
yingyinNormal.zh: 而做产品可以是看做完成一次使命专注于质量、理念，以及人们的内心...

yingyinNormal.en: So, you know how it's not just family time that matters. It's quality family time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你知道重要的不只是跟家人一起的时间，而是高质量的家人共处时光。

yingyinNormal.en: And so the CDOs that you create are of the highest quality and the highest value. Absolutely. Yep. Absolutely.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你发行的债务担保是质量最好价值最高的。绝对的。绝对的。

yingyinNormal.en: President Stenborg, you make it sound like you don't care about the quality of the education. Is that true?
yingyinNormal.zh: 斯滕堡校长，你说的这些让人觉得你好像根本不在乎教育的质量，是这样吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Granted, my methods may have been somewhat unorthodox, but I think the end result will be a measurable enhancement to penny's quality of life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就算是吧，我的方法可能有点唐突，但是我认为这能很好的提高佩妮的生活质量。

yingyinNormal.en: There's more. The applications go beyond the disease. There are indications that show that therapy can improve cognitive functioning, memory quality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有这种药物的作用已经不止于治病，有迹象表明该疗法能改善认知机能和记忆质量。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Rise of the Planet of the Apes》

yingyinNormal.en: But through no one's fault, Penny, the quality of dinner conversation in this apartment has declined. And again, I'm looking at no one in particular, Penny.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然没人有错，佩妮，但晚餐谈话的质量的确下滑了。再次重申，这事谁都不怪，佩妮。

yingyinNormal.en: Penny, this is your enterprise, so it's ultimately your decision, but based on the quality of his work, I'd strongly recommend that we let Leonard go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩妮，这是你的公司，所以最终决议权在于你，但基于他工作的质量，我强烈建议开除莱纳德。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, These genomes, these 23 chromosomes, they don't in any way represent the quality of our relationships or the nature of our society, at least not yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个，这些基因组，这23个染色体它们并不代表我们人际关系的质量，或者我们这个社会的性质，至少目前还没有。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, that isn't necessary. No, it is. Leonard pointed out to me that I'm not always a loving and supportive boyfriend, so here's some quality luggage. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，你不用这么做。不，我需要。莱纳德告诉我我并不是一个时常能给予你爱与支持的男朋友，所以我给你买了高质量的行李箱。谢谢。

yingyinNormal.en: No, not so fast there, OK. You make a quality offer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别急、别急，你开的条件不错。

yingyinNormal.en: Bert did quality research. And he deserves whatever accolades he receives.
yingyinNormal.zh: 伯特的研究做得不错，他受到表彰也是理所当然的。

yingyinNormal.en: Ava has quality I like. You're kidding me? She's just like my friend Marisol.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾娃身上有我喜欢的特质。你逗我呢吧？她很像我的朋友玛丽索。

yingyinNormal.en: Manhattan is the best place to buy quality Christmas gifts. We have 40 bucks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 曼哈顿是最适合买好圣诞礼物的地方了，我们有四十块钱。

yingyinNormal.en: Why is it inside out? Excuse me. But this is a purebred, show-quality Sphinx cat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它的皮怎么翻出来了？帮帮忙，这可是展示级的纯种斯芬克斯猫。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: an essential and distinguishing attribute of something or someone

examination_example.sentence: All good targets should have multiple criteria relating to critical factors such as time, money, <highlight>quality</highlight> and customer feedback.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 所有好的目标都应该有与关键因素相关的多重标准，例如时间、金钱、质量和客户反馈。

examination_example.sentence: Never mind the <highlight>quality</highlight>, then, count the number.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 质量无所谓，数量最重要。

examination_example.sentence: First, consumers may take CSR spending as a "signal" that a company's products are of high <highlight>quality</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 首先，消费者可能会将企业社会责任支出视为公司产品高质量的“信号”。

sense_info_list.en: a degree or grade of excellence or worth

examination_example.sentence: It is in pursuit of <highlight>quality</highlight> service.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它追求的是优质服务。

examination_example.sentence: The food police are determined that this enjoyment should be rendered yet another <highlight>quality</highlight> pleasure guaranteed to damage our health.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 食品监管局确信这种乐趣又是另一种必定会损害我们健康的“罪恶的”快乐。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Quality</highlight> service.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 优质服务。

sense_info_list.en: a distinctive attribute or characteristic possessed by someone or something

examination_example.sentence: People should look to intangible <highlight>qualities</highlight> like character and intellect rather than dieting their way to size zero or wasp-waist physiques.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人们应该关注像性格和智力这样的无形品质，而不是节食减肥到零号身材或蜂腰身材。

examination_example.sentence: I find courage an essential <highlight>quality</highlight> for the understanding, let alone the performance, of his works.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我发现对于理解他的作品来说，勇气是一个很重要的品质，更不必说演奏他的作品了。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: an essential and distinguishing attribute of something or someone

examination_example.sentence: It effectively improves the learning <highlight>quality</highlight> of students in rural areas.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有效地提高了农村学生的学习质量。

examination_example.sentence: Studies found that in remote areas the poor <highlight>quality</highlight> or lack of Internet access can put students at a disadvantage.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究发现，在偏远地区，互联网质量差或缺乏互联网接入可能会使学生处于不利地位。

examination_example.sentence: This includes the impact of short-term lets on housing costs and <highlight>quality</highlight> of life for residents.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这包括短期出租对居民住房成本和生活质量的影响。

sense_info_list.en: a distinctive attribute or characteristic possessed by someone or something

examination_example.sentence: This teaches them to be understanding of and sympathetic towards others—<highlight>qualities</highlight> sure to take them a long way in life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这教导他们理解和同情他人，这些品质一定能让他们的人生之路走得长远。

examination_example.sentence: It is a <highlight>quality</highlight> that is required of artists, but it is also present in the lives of scientists and entrepreneurs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是艺术家必须具备的品质，但它也存在于科学家和企业家的生活中。

examination_example.sentence: This mysterious—but teachable—<highlight>quality</highlight> is creativity, the subject of a recently-published report by Durham Commission on Creativity and Education.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这种神秘但可以教授的品质，就是创造力。这是达勒姆创意与教育委员会最近发表的一份报告的主题。

sense_info_list.en: a degree or grade of excellence or worth
sense_info_list.zh: 优质; 优选的; 高质量的

examination_example.sentence: Failure to spend sufficient <highlight>quality</highlight> time with them.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 没有花足够的时间和他们相处。

examination_example.sentence: Parents can't or don't spend enough <highlight>quality</highlight> time with their kids.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 父母不能或没有花足够优质的时间陪伴孩子。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

sense_info_list.en: an essential and distinguishing attribute of something or someone

examination_example.sentence: Its <highlight>quality</highlight> is usually guaranteed.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它的质量通常是有保证的。

examination_example.sentence: The system Medicare developed to rate nursing home <highlight>quality</highlight> is of little help to finding a satisfactory place.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为评估疗养院质量而开发的医疗保险系统对找到一个令人满意的地方几乎没有帮助。

examination_example.sentence: They will pay more attention to the <highlight>quality</highlight> of their products.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们将会更加注意产品的质量。

sense_info_list.en: a distinctive attribute or characteristic possessed by someone or something

examination_example.sentence: But researchers have come to realize that being humble generally indicates the presence of deeply admirable personal <highlight>qualities</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但研究人员已经意识到，谦虚通常意味着拥有极其令人钦佩的个人品质。

examination_example.sentence: Creativity and adaptability are desirable <highlight>qualities</highlight> in today's workplace.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 创造力和适应能力是当今职场所需的理想品质。

examination_example.sentence: Blue is associated with the positive <highlight>qualities</highlight> of trust, efficiency, quietness, coolness, reflection and calm.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 蓝色与信任、效率、安静、冷静、思考和平静等积极品质联系在一起。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: an essential and distinguishing attribute of something or someone

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>quality</highlight> of grassland will be tracked by monitoring the shape, color and texture (质地) of grass.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 将通过监测草的形状、颜色和质地来跟踪草地的质量。

examination_example.sentence: According to recent studies, the answer is a big YES, if the air <highlight>quality</highlight> in your camping area is good.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据最近的研究，如果你露营地的空气质量良好的话，答案是特别肯定的。

examination_example.sentence: Every day he makes sure that fresh vegetables and high <highlight>quality</highlight> oil are used for cooking.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他每天都确保用新鲜的蔬菜和高质量的油来烹饪。

sense_info_list.en: a distinctive attribute or characteristic possessed by someone or something

examination_example.sentence: It refers to a person's positive <highlight>qualities</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它指的是一个人的积极品质。

examination_example.sentence: Boasting about yourself, and your best <highlight>qualities</highlight> is very difficult for a child who came into the classroom not feeling confident.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于一个在课堂上没有自信的孩子来说，吹嘘自己和自己最好的品质是非常困难的。

examination_example.sentence: Both of us had the <highlight>qualities</highlight> and virtues that are typical of American actors: humorous, aggressive, and making fun of each other.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们两个都有着美国演员典型的品格和美德：幽默，进取，爱彼此打趣。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 良好质量；好品质；良好素质
低品质；素质低；质量低下

sense_info_list.en: an essential and distinguishing attribute of something or someone

examination_example.sentence: The comfortable shirt I bought yesterday is made of fine good high <highlight>quality</highlight> cotton from Xinjiang, China.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我昨天买的这件舒适的衬衫是用来自中国新疆的优质棉花制成的。

examination_example.sentence: Choose one good <highlight>quality</highlight> of pigs and give some examples to prove it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 选择一种品种好的猪，并举例证明。

examination_example.sentence: And researchers need to examine differences according to the nature and <highlight>quality</highlight> of green space.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究人员需要根据绿色空间的性质和质量来检查差异。

sense_info_list.en: a distinctive attribute or characteristic possessed by someone or something

examination_example.sentence: I admire Li for many of her good <highlight>qualities</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我因李的许多优点钦佩她。

examination_example.sentence: As long as you have these <highlight>qualities</highlight> mentioned above, you will be excellent and make a difference to the world.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 只要你具备上面提到的这些品质，你就会很优秀，并对世界产生影响。

examination_example.sentence: Listening silently is a good <highlight>quality</highlight> that we should have.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 静听是我们应该具备的良好品质。

examination_example.sentence: "He's a <highlight>quality</highlight> horse and if you want him for cab work, he's a bargain. "
examination_example.sentence_trans: “他是匹好马，如果你想让他做马车，他就成了便宜货。”
